Component	Version	Purpose
Java JDK	17 or newer	Core language runtime
JavaFX SDK	17+ (e.g., 23.0.1)	GUI framework for building desktop apps

üí° Note: JavaFX is no longer bundled with most JDKs (Adoptium, OpenJDK, Corretto, etc.), so it must be downloaded separately.

üîó Installation Links

JavaFX SDK: https://openjfx.io

Download the latest SDK for your OS and unzip it to a known location (e.g. C:\javafx on Windows).

JDK (Eclipse Adoptium): https://adoptium.net

Install the latest LTS version (e.g. JDK 21 or newer).
